#Privacy Policy Summary for PenPort

PenPort, developed by the National Pensions Authority of Ghana, is a platform that allows users to monitor their pension contributions, view account details, and receive important notifications. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring your personal information is secure.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect the following information:

Personal Details: Name, email, contact number, date of birth, and pension account details.
Usage Data: Device information, app usage patterns, and IP address.
Notification Preferences: Your choices regarding reminders and updates.
2. How We Use Your Information
Your information helps us:

Provide access to your pension details.
Notify you about updates and contributions.
Improve app functionality and services.
Comply with legal obligations.
3. Data Security
We use encryption, secure servers, and regular security updates to protect your data. However, no system is entirely foolproof, so we encourage you to safeguard your login credentials.

4. Your Rights
You can:

Access and update your data.
Request data deletion.
Adjust notification preferences.
Contact us at info@npra.gov.gh or call us at +233 (302) 968 692 / +233 (302) 968 693 / 0800766000 (MTN Toll Free) for assistance.

5. Sharing Information
We only share your data:

With trusted service providers.
When legally required.
With your explicit consent.
6. Updates to This Policy
We may update this policy occasionally. The latest version will always be available in the app or on our website.

For questions or concerns, contact us at:

Email: info@npra.gov.gh
Address: National Pensions Authority, Ghana
Phone:  +233 (302) 968 692 / +233 (302) 968 693 / 0800766000 (MTN Toll Free)
By using PenPort, you agree to this Privacy Policy.
